soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomE

Class FullSensitiveNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomPA.IVarAbstraction
      • soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomE.FullSensitiveNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Numberable

    public class FullSensitiveNode
extends IVarAbstraction
    This class defines an abstract pointer in the geometric points-to solver. All the points-to/flows-to information and the load/store constraints related to this pointer are stored here. The pointer assignment inference rules and the complex constraints initialization rules are also implemented here.
    Author:
    xiao
